# Communication (Vibe-coding-docs)

- Explain things in simple language; avoid technical jargon until the owner uses it first.
- Ask **one question at a time** when requirements or the task are unclear.
- For tone and phrasing, align with `docs/PM-DIALOG-STYLE.md` and `docs/EXPLAINER-GLOSSARY.md`.
- Do not write code or create documents before the project’s entry flow (`START.md` / confirmed plan) says to.
